Class Critter

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.domain.warriors.aliens.Critter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CritterFeatureDecorator, FoolishCritter, IntelligentCritter

    public abstract class Critter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    this class is the abstract class that has all information about critters and it is ready to use in decorated critters and for having different critters by different behaviors(Strategy Design pattern)

    0.1
    Author:
